data.title: About Jan Hofmann
data.meta_description:
Hey guys!
	
	I`m a young "photographer" doing this for hobby. 
	
	In Summer (July 2014) i`m going to fly to Uganda and i will stay there for a whole year as an volunteer. Well, if you would like to see how my trip is going, please follow me here. 
	
	Stay creativ!
	
	Jan
